== 制片 ==
《落叶归根》由星皓娱乐和Fortissimo Films赞助，由Fortissimo的彼得·洛赫尔和[[伍特·巴伦德雷希特|伍特·巴伦德雷希特]]制片。<ref name=Rothrock>{{cite web|url=https://www.variety.com/article/VR1117940175.html?categoryid=1043&cs=1|title=Film pair get some 'Air' in China|author=Rothrock, Vicki|publisher=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|accessdate=2007-12-06|date=2006-03-22}}</ref>这是张扬和星皓娱乐的首次合作，却是和Fortissimo Films的第五次合作。<ref name=Rothrock/>

尽管电影展示的是老赵从深圳到重庆的长途跋涉，但大部分拍摄在[[云南|云南]]进行。<ref name=Elley>{{cite web|url=http://www.variety.com/index.asp?layout=features2007&content=jump&jump=review&dept=berlin&nav=Rberlin&articleid=VE1117933051|title=Getting Home|publisher=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|author = Elley, Derek|date=2007-03-12|accessdate=2007-09-16}}</ref>

== 反响 ==
2007年2月11日，《落叶归根》在当年的[[柏林国际电影节|柏林国际电影节]]作为电影展系列的一部分上映，这是它在西方的首映。它获得了[[評審團特別獎|評審團特別獎]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.variety.com/index.asp?layout=features2007&content=jump&jump=story&dept=berlin&nav=Nberlin&articleid=VR1117959774|title= "Tuya" nabs top prize at Berlin fest|author=Meza, Ed|publisher=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=2007-02-17|accessdate=2007-09-16}}</ref>随后，它又在[[絲綢銀幕：美國亞裔電影節|絲綢銀幕：美國亞裔電影節]]、[[多维尔亚洲电影节|多维尔亚洲电影节]]、<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dianying.com/en/news/view/254|title="Director's debut film enters Deauville"|publisher=Chinese Movie Database|date=2007-03-27|accessdate=2007-09-16}}</ref>[[纽约亚洲电影节|纽约亚洲电影节]]等场合上映。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.subwaycinema.com/frames/nyaff07_home.htm|title=NYAFF 2007 Films: Getting Home|publisher = [[New_York_Asian_Film_Festival|New York Asian Film Festival]]|accessdate=2007-09-16 |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070824005434/http://subwaycinema.com/frames/nyaff07_home.htm <!-- Bot retrieved archive --> |archivedate = 2007-08-24}}</ref>

同时，西方也有对《落叶归根》的评论，一些人认为该片让他们想起了美国喜剧《[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Weekend_at_Bernie%27s 老板度假去]》，且在情节、角色和戏剧上远胜后者。一则评论如是评价《落叶归根》：“一部完美的有坡度的、温暖人心的关于友情和承诺的戏剧，带着一点黑色幽默。”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.firecracker-media.com/features/berlin2007.shtml|title=Cyborgs and Samurai:The Berlin Film Festival|author=North, Nick|publisher=Firecracker Features|accessdate=2007-09-16 |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070319210829/http://www.firecracker-media.com/features/berlin2007.shtml <!-- Bot retrieved archive --> |archivedate = 2007-03-19}}</ref>同时，一些杂志如《[[综艺|综艺]]》《[[That's_Beijing|That's Beijing]]》也分别表扬赵本山在片中“表现精准”“生动”。<ref name=Wong/><ref name=Elley/>

